    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迷你市场模拟器 VR</strong></h2>欢迎来到迷你市场模拟器 VR。   这是终极虚拟现实体验，您可以在其中实现自己的企业梦想，通过在虚拟现实中经营和扩展您自己的迷你市场！沉浸于繁忙的零售环境中，您的每一个决策都将塑造您通向成功市场之路。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特点</strong></h2>在虚拟现实中体验完全沉浸式的3D迷你市场。 使用VR控制器处理物品，扫描产品，并管理任务，所有这些都具有逼真的互动。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸感强且逼真的环境</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/eddb2937dc7e04765222f72ea36aa4b2.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/eddb2937dc7e04765222f72ea36aa4b2.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/eddb2937dc7e04765222f72ea36aa4b2.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >互动式虚拟现实游戏</h2>参与高度互动的虚拟现实游戏系统，您可以执行多种任务，如为顾客结账、管理库存和处理店铺事件。 每项任务都设计成亲身参与，利用虚拟现实的功能，使每一个动作都能让人感到真实和有成就感。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/cd03257dd4f28e1529218e0f02a67161.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/cd03257dd4f28e1529218e0f02a67161.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/cd03257dd4f28e1529218e0f02a67161.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制化的店铺布局</h2>根据您的风格和策略定制店铺布局。 重新排列货架、展示架和柜台，优化购物体验并提高效率。 根据不同顾客偏好和业务目标，定制店铺的外观和功能，打造独特、个性化的迷你市场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/31ee25e29de499059ba531f85414b16e.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/31ee25e29de499059ba531f85414b16e.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/31ee25e29de499059ba531f85414b16e.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩展产品和家具</h2>享受不断扩展的店铺产品和家具库。 定期更新引入新的物品和装饰，让您的迷你市场保持新鲜和吸引人。 从季节性产品到独特的家具，不断增强您的店铺，让顾客乐此不疲地回来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/4b4c7cf3d1c6501208cde7a410261017.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/4b4c7cf3d1c6501208cde7a410261017.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/4b4c7cf3d1c6501208cde7a410261017.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >清洁游戏玩法</h2>利用清洁游戏玩法功能保持店铺的清洁。 扫地、擦拭墙壁上的涂鸦，并清理垃圾，确保一个愉快的购物环境。 清洁度影响顾客满意度和店铺声誉，为游戏增添了更多现实感和管理层面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/2555a210e0356d0d61e5425ce131dba3.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/2555a210e0356d0d61e5425ce131dba3.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/2555a210e0356d0d61e5425ce131dba3.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小游戏</h2>享受额外的小游戏乐趣，包括篮球小游戏，在那里您可以休息一下并投篮。 期待我们计划在未来更新中添加更多的小游戏，为游戏增添多样性和额外的娱乐性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/1aea716e2d9e5903c48cadca7be90c99.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/1aea716e2d9e5903c48cadca7be90c99.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/1aea716e2d9e5903c48cadca7be90c99.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>加入我们的Discord频道<br>",
